com.reactivecascade.i

Interface IBaseAction<PHANTOM_OUT>

  • Type Parameters:
    PHANTOM_OUT - is not strictly needed, but helps the IDE tooling with generics
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IAction<PHANTOM_OUT>, IActionOne<IN>, IActionOneR<IN,OUT>, IActionR<OUT>, IActionTwo<IN1,IN2>, IActionTwoR<IN1,IN2,OUT>

    public interface IBaseAction<PHANTOM_OUT>
    This is a marker interface which other functional interfaces extend

    Implementing this interface indicates a primary mOnFireAction, usually one executed asynchronously on an IThreadType
